# This repo is LF-canonical: VLC 3.x embeds Lua 5.1 (LF) and the headless dialog suite
# diffs the widget grid against test/dialog_layout.snapshot. Without this, a Windows
# clone (core.autocrlf=true) checks the snapshot out as CRLF and the suite fails on the
# invisible \r even though the layout is byte-identical. Force LF on checkout everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf
